[DOOR CLOSES]

41:41.265 --> 41:44.268
Hey, my car is making
that clicking sound again.

41:44.301 --> 41:45.702
<i> ♪ Never gonna
let you go</i>

41:45.736 --> 41:47.905
Hey, now.

41:45.736 --> 41:47.905
[THOMAS CHUCKLES]

41:47.938 --> 41:49.640
What's the occasion?

41:49.673 --> 41:52.409
To celebrate your car
making that clicking sound.

41:52.442 --> 41:54.711
How was your day?

41:52.442 --> 41:54.711
[GROANS]

41:54.745 --> 41:57.248
Aw, come here.
Welcome home. Mm.

41:57.281 --> 42:00.017
[PHONE RINGING]

42:00.050 --> 42:02.018
I should probably get that,
just in case it's a job.

42:02.052 --> 42:04.320
Yes, yes, yes, yes.

42:04.354 --> 42:06.189
This is nice.

42:04.354 --> 42:06.189
Yeah.

42:06.222 --> 42:07.924
Girls, dinner, come on!

42:07.958 --> 42:08.993
CLEO: Hello?

42:10.594 --> 42:13.163
THOMAS: Henry.

42:13.196 --> 42:14.965
Madam.

42:16.299 --> 42:17.601
Jenna.

42:25.909 --> 42:27.311
<i> Madame.</i>

42:27.344 --> 42:29.980
Ooh, sparkling cider.

