42:48.632 --> 42:51.001
CLEO: Bye. Thank you.

42:52.136 --> 42:53.436
Bill Boone is dead.

42:53.470 --> 42:56.073
[TENSE MUSIC]

42:56.106 --> 42:57.107
What?

42:57.140 --> 42:59.376
Lucas just confessed
to killing him.

42:59.409 --> 43:01.511
[CLEO SIGHS]

43:01.544 --> 43:03.280
I just saw Lucas.

43:03.313 --> 43:04.481
What? When?

43:04.515 --> 43:06.383
The other day at The Yolk.

43:06.417 --> 43:08.084
He seemed like...
I don't know. I...

43:08.118 --> 43:10.420
I can't believe it.

43:10.453 --> 43:12.990
I think that it's
a good thing

43:13.023 --> 43:16.493
that Bill's not out there
anymore, that we are safe.

43:16.526 --> 43:17.962
Yeah.

43:20.330 --> 43:25.135
That this is finally,

43:25.169 --> 43:28.205
finally over.

43:28.238 --> 43:29.739
[CIDER POURING]

43:29.773 --> 43:32.643
Right.

43:29.773 --> 43:32.643
CLEO: Of course, yes.

43:34.178 --> 43:36.413
THOMAS: Okay.

43:36.446 --> 43:38.015
Okay, then.

43:38.048 --> 43:39.849
Now, Jenna,

43:39.883 --> 43:44.622
how...how was
school today?

43:50.694 --> 43:52.362
I'm failing.

43:52.396 --> 43:54.331
[CHUCKLES]

43:58.869 --> 44:00.170
What?

44:00.204 --> 44:02.639
I'm failing school.

44:02.673 --> 44:04.207
They told me today.

44:04.240 --> 44:08.077
Okay, how...wait.
Okay, wait, wait, wait.

44:08.111 --> 44:10.513
They told you that you're
failing what subject?

44:10.547 --> 44:12.149
All of them.

44:15.018 --> 44:17.855
I don't know.
I don't know how it happened.

44:19.757 --> 44:22.759
What if I don't get
into Colgate or...anywhere?

44:22.792 --> 44:24.827
I mean, I had a plan.

44:24.861 --> 44:27.063
Jenna, it's gonna be okay.

44:27.096 --> 44:29.433
Grades aren't, like,
the end of the world.

44:29.466 --> 44:31.968
Yeah, maybe to you,
they're not, but I actually
have a future, Henry.

44:32.001 --> 44:33.203
THOMAS: Whoa, sweetie...

44:32.001 --> 44:33.203
CLEO: Jenna...

44:33.236 --> 44:34.805
No, I know my life
is some sort of joke to you.

44:36.039 --> 44:37.807
That's not what I was saying.

44:37.841 --> 44:40.143
This is your fault.

44:40.177 --> 44:41.311
What?

44:41.345 --> 44:43.647
Everybody takes care of you,

44:43.680 --> 44:45.248
and you don't even give a shit.

44:45.281 --> 44:47.383
I mean, my own dad
told me to take care of you.

44:47.417 --> 44:50.153
And that's my fault?

44:47.417 --> 44:50.153
Yes.

44:50.186 --> 44:53.256
Henry dragged Jenna
off to a party.

44:53.289 --> 44:55.058
Henry was acting out.
Jenna followed suit.

44:55.091 --> 44:57.327
I took care of it.

44:55.091 --> 44:57.327
Followed suit?

44:57.360 --> 44:59.363
What?

44:57.360 --> 44:59.363
Well, come on.

44:59.396 --> 45:00.530
She must have had
some influence.

45:00.563 --> 45:02.565
Dude, I'm sitting right here.

45:02.599 --> 45:03.867
Why do you say that?

45:03.900 --> 45:06.503
Oh, sneaking off to parties,

45:06.536 --> 45:07.671
failing classes.

45:07.704 --> 45:09.606
Jenna was not like this before.

45:09.639 --> 45:11.341
[SCOFFS]
Wow, okay.

45:11.375 --> 45:15.479
No, he's right.
Everything was fine
before you got here.

45:15.512 --> 45:17.647
Jenna, what the fuck?

45:17.680 --> 45:19.048
This is your shit.

45:19.082 --> 45:20.984
Don't try to make this
about me.

45:21.017 --> 45:23.186
Right, I'm sorry,
that's your job.

45:23.219 --> 45:26.223
I didn't ask you to, like,
hang out with me

45:26.256 --> 45:28.491
or help me
or whatever the fuck it is

45:28.524 --> 45:30.127
you think that I'm doing.

45:30.160 --> 45:31.795
I have no choice!

45:31.828 --> 45:33.330
I mean, you live in my house.

45:33.363 --> 45:35.432
Jenna.

45:33.363 --> 45:35.432
Hey, don't.

45:35.465 --> 45:38.468
So you can criticize
my daughter,
but I can't interrupt yours?

45:38.501 --> 45:41.638
I just want to hear her out.
It's not a bad thing to listen.

45:41.671 --> 45:43.606
As if I don't?

45:41.671 --> 45:43.606
No. [SIGHS]

45:43.640 --> 45:46.710
All I'm saying is that someone
has to maintain a sense
of normalcy around here.

45:46.743 --> 45:49.079
[SCOFFS] What the hell
do you mean by that?

45:49.112 --> 45:50.847
Nothing.

45:50.881 --> 45:53.416
Nothing, it's just...
you know, it's a lot sometimes.

45:53.449 --> 45:55.084
What is, being with me?

45:55.118 --> 45:57.154
No, no, just
parenting everybody.

45:57.187 --> 46:00.023
Jesus, Thomas, you act like
I'm not as good as you.

46:00.056 --> 46:03.192
No, we...Cleo, we just have
a different version of good.

46:03.226 --> 46:05.629
Are you fucking serious?

46:03.226 --> 46:05.629
Dude, lay off.

46:05.662 --> 46:07.430
He's not talking to you.

46:05.662 --> 46:07.430
Here we go.

46:07.464 --> 46:09.799
Here we go?

46:07.464 --> 46:09.799
Yeah, this is exactly
what I'm talking about.

46:09.832 --> 46:11.068
The two of you
are going at it again.

46:11.101 --> 46:13.136
You two love to pick fights.

46:13.170 --> 46:14.671
Will you please
keep her out of this?

46:14.705 --> 46:16.372
She's already in it!

46:14.705 --> 46:16.372
You know what? Fuck this.

46:16.406 --> 46:18.408
Yeah, run away.
That'll make everything better.

46:18.441 --> 46:19.709
Whatever works for you, Henry.

46:19.743 --> 46:22.312
Okay.

46:19.743 --> 46:22.312
What did you say to him?

46:22.345 --> 46:24.648
Huh? To get him
to blow up his whole life.

46:24.681 --> 46:26.750
Is it the same shit
you say to me?

46:26.783 --> 46:29.753
Jenna, I am not
responsible for you.

46:29.786 --> 46:31.855
Just like you are not
responsible for me.

46:31.888 --> 46:33.156
Aren't I, though?

46:33.189 --> 46:35.525
Who else is going
to keep your secrets?

46:35.559 --> 46:38.161
You know what?
I am so tired

46:38.195 --> 46:40.764
of telling your
stupid fucking lies.

46:40.797 --> 46:43.766
You...you made me
into someone I'm not,

46:43.800 --> 46:45.735
and you just use people up
and spit them out.

46:45.768 --> 46:47.737
What the fuck?
No, I don't.

46:47.770 --> 46:49.873
You know exactly
what you are.

46:49.906 --> 46:51.274
You're just afraid
to admit it.

46:51.307 --> 46:53.076
Jenna, you better
fucking watch it.

46:53.110 --> 46:54.744
Or what?

46:53.110 --> 46:54.744
THOMAS: Hey!

46:54.778 --> 46:56.846
CLEO: What the hell
is going on?

46:56.880 --> 46:59.149
[TENSE MUSIC]

46:59.182 --> 47:01.685
Well?

47:01.718 --> 47:03.453
Henry's...

47:01.718 --> 47:03.453
Jenna's gay.

47:13.630 --> 47:15.665
[STAMMERS]

47:15.698 --> 47:17.333
Jenna...

47:17.367 --> 47:19.736
THOMAS: Henry, give her
a little bit of space, Jesus!

47:19.769 --> 47:21.371
What is wrong with you?
Look what you did.

47:21.405 --> 47:23.340
What she did?
They're both out of control.

47:23.373 --> 47:24.874
How come only one of them
is crying?

47:24.908 --> 47:26.743
You are so fucking blind,
Thomas, you know that?

47:26.776 --> 47:28.579
Henry, come on, let's go.

47:30.013 --> 47:32.115
Un-fucking-believable.

47:35.752 --> 47:37.855
[CELL DOORS CLANG]

47:39.923 --> 47:41.992
[KEYS JANGLE]

47:42.793 --> 47:44.928
[DOOR CLOSES]

47:44.962 --> 47:48.098
[SOMBER MUSIC]

48:14.491 --> 48:17.394
[CELL PHONE CHIMING]

48:25.635 --> 48:28.338
Wendy, hi.
Everything okay?

48:30.373 --> 48:32.342
Lucas?

48:32.375 --> 48:33.911
He what?

48:36.045 --> 48:38.348
[SIGHS] No, hold on.
Slow down. I...

48:40.249 --> 48:43.586
No, I didn't know.
I've...

48:43.619 --> 48:45.522
I've been on leave.

48:47.323 --> 48:49.393
Let me find out
everything I can.

48:58.935 --> 49:01.972
[MUSIC PLAYING SOFTLY
OVER RADIO]

49:20.457 --> 49:21.658
Is that Jenna?

49:23.326 --> 49:25.095
No, it's work.

49:27.631 --> 49:29.032
You okay?

49:33.236 --> 49:36.974
You're not a bad influence
or a bad person.

49:38.508 --> 49:40.177
Really.

49:42.045 --> 49:44.414
I just totally betrayed Jenna.

49:45.882 --> 49:48.352
So that's true?
Jenna's gay?

49:55.091 --> 49:58.362
I should never have said that.

49:58.395 --> 50:00.330
She trusted me.

50:04.233 --> 50:06.737
I say things I shouldn't say
all the time.

50:08.404 --> 50:09.740
I know.

50:11.040 --> 50:14.043
We Coles women
are complicated.

50:14.076 --> 50:17.313
I think you mean flawed.

50:17.347 --> 50:20.417
Yeah, but flawed together.

50:29.226 --> 50:32.329
[SUSPENSEFUL MUSIC]

51:27.217 --> 51:30.320
[DRAMATIC MUSIC]

51:34.423 --> 51:36.760
TOWNES:<i> My is
Townes Atticus Linderman,</i>

51:36.793 --> 51:41.497
<i> and if you're watching this,
I'm probably dead.</i>

51:41.531 --> 51:44.133
I'm about to embark
on something new,

51:44.167 --> 51:46.837
something that I hope
will help more than hurt,

51:46.870 --> 51:48.371
but I'm not sure.

51:48.404 --> 51:50.540
[ELECTRONIC ROCK MUSIC]

51:50.573 --> 51:54.344
<i> There are things I've seen
that I never knew
were possible,</i>

51:54.377 --> 51:57.747
<i> though I always
hoped they were.</i>

51:57.780 --> 52:00.784
<i> Some people might want
to use it to hurt others,</i>

52:00.817 --> 52:03.786
<i> and I just...</i>

52:03.820 --> 52:06.723
<i> I can't let that happen.</i>

52:06.756 --> 52:10.627
<i> ♪ ♪</i>

52:10.660 --> 52:13.897
<i> [SOFT MUSIC PLAYING]</i>

52:28.044 --> 52:31.013
TOWNES:<i> So if this leads
to my end,</i>

52:31.046 --> 52:32.849
<i> to whoever's watching this,</i>

52:32.882 --> 52:36.319
<i> tell my parents
and Megan I'll miss them.</i>

52:40.256 --> 52:42.726
I hope you understand
my choices.

52:43.493 --> 52:45.195
Jenna,

52:45.228 --> 52:48.698
it was a pleasure
serving by your side.

52:48.731 --> 52:50.867
You are my friend,

52:50.900 --> 52:53.936
even if you are stubborn

52:53.970 --> 52:56.406
and opinionated.

52:57.674 --> 53:00.310
And, Henry Coles,

53:00.343 --> 53:03.880
thank you for trusting me
and for confiding in me.

53:05.481 --> 53:09.486
I hope whatever killed me
helped you...

53:09.519 --> 53:14.357
or people like you
or people in general.

53:19.095 --> 53:21.231
And, Zoe...

53:25.968 --> 53:29.239
You made me brave.

53:29.272 --> 53:31.408
I love you.

53:41.618 --> 53:43.787
[BREATHES DEEPLY]

53:55.899 --> 53:58.468
Why did you cover
your art?

54:01.070 --> 54:02.739
I don't know.

54:04.473 --> 54:08.077
I guess I was feeling stuck...

54:08.111 --> 54:11.147
needed a change.

54:11.180 --> 54:13.149
Did it help?

54:13.182 --> 54:14.818
Not really.

54:17.720 --> 54:20.724
I'm sorry things have been
so chaotic lately.

54:23.226 --> 54:25.428
It's okay.

54:23.226 --> 54:25.428
No, it's not.

54:27.463 --> 54:30.433
You deserve to have a home
that feels secure.

54:31.501 --> 54:35.171
We moved around so much.

54:35.204 --> 54:37.540
I've tried to give
you that, but...

54:40.543 --> 54:43.013
I'm gonna do better, Henry.
I promise.

54:47.149 --> 54:49.886
It's you.

54:49.919 --> 54:51.121
What is?

54:51.154 --> 54:55.058
[SOFT DRAMATIC MUSIC]

54:55.091 --> 54:58.027
Doesn't matter where we go.

54:58.060 --> 55:00.597
This room doesn't matter.

55:02.398 --> 55:04.767
It's you.
You're my home.

55:04.801 --> 55:07.671
You're what
makes me feel safe.

